4a1696477483cf1236a2ab80ffc6e2c7ea68232d.query:
INSERT INTO scripting_schema (queen_tag, schema_message_packed)
    VALUES ($1, $2)
    ON CONFLICT (queen_tag)
    DO UPDATE SET 
    schema_message_packed=$2

4e3a1edab0d5a2ae55c0933e631ff761cf1cb231.query:
INSERT INTO world_output (queen_tag, world_time, payload)
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3);

5e69d1a4c38e65556975327af9e22f24bfbc5088.query:
SELECT value_message_packed
    FROM world
    WHERE field=$1

9dd075ae8eb7861875ce80eb7ce713f279602de1.query:
INSERT INTO world (field, queen_tag, world_timestamp,value_message_packed)
    VALUES ($1, $4, $2, $3)
    ON CONFLICT (field, queen_tag) 
    DO UPDATE
    SET value_message_packed=$3, world_timestamp=$2, updated=now()
